node.text: When the fish is ready to say goodbye 👋🏻 🎣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Captain Katherine Salom in Houston, Texas. May be an image of 1 person, standing, tree and outdoors.

node.text: Still feeling super tired and sick from the rona😷👎🏻 Spending most of my time just resting and trying to get better because I need to get back to fishing!🎣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Captain Katherine Salom in Houston, Texas with @fourhorsementackle. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Happy Friday y’all!☀️ I’m wishing I was fishing, but I’m hanging out on the couch trying to get better🤒 Y’all have a great weekend!🙌🏻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Captain Katherine Salom in Houston, Texas with @countryoutfitter, and @roperworld. May be an image of 1 person, standing, boots and outdoors.

node.text: While everyone is at @icastshow I’m stuck at home sick😭😷 Feeling some major FOMO right now!👎🏻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Captain Katherine Salom in Houston, Texas. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: It’s a rainy day in Houston today, so I’m trying to get caught up on everything I’ve been behind on😅 So here’s a pic from this weekend when we were hanging out in Austin, TX🤠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Captain Katherine Salom in Houston, Texas with @xtratuf, and @toadfishoutfitters. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: I like big reds and I cannot lie🎣🔥
